These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
City: marseilles, london
1. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
2. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Food          | spinach | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| City   | marseilles  | london      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, woodworking
City: hamburg, boston
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
3. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Hobby       | filmmaking         | woodworking |
| City         | boston | hamburg   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, thriller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, writing
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Hobby           | puzzles        | writing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, kale
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
3. the person eating kale is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Food     | kale   | strawberry |

