There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Sport         | volleyball | sailing     |
| Beverage     | juice | iced-tea  |

