The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, mechanic
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, turkish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, rowing
1. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the chef##8
2. the mechanic is on the left or right of the chinese##3
3. the chinese is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
4. the chef is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |
| House         | gothic-revival  | townhouse  |
| Job           | chef    | mechanic |
| Nationality   | chinese | turkish  |
| Sport         | rowing  | climbing |

